10 F.title: Thought Experiment- VR Travel App
introductions: I want to make a travel app which helps users visit places which are aggregated by city so that you can for example visit Austin without being here. The app will have a list of cities to visit and within them places you can look and walk around.
360 images give users a more immersive experience when viewed through a VR headset such as Google Cardboard. Before building the app I thought of my target audience and made a persona.
